{"tid":1638764,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Use #AskLIHKG to ask us anything!","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T08:50:16.000Z","uid":243366,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"175f6e5eba1c8296a9c24583a11ffa215de4f14a","tid":1638764,"uid":243366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:57:22.000Z","msg":"Hello fellow hoomans from around the 🌍 <br />\nWelcome to LIHKG <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIf you guys have anything I mean ANYTHING that you wanna ask us, whether it&rsquo;s about this cute little piggy <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, weird stuff you recently found out about HK or things related to #HKprotests, feel free to use the hashtag #AskLIHKG on twitter to reach us. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe&rsquo;ll screen cap it and post it here for fellow <br />\nLIHKGers to answer your question. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEnjoy this silly yet rebellious forum. I&rsquo;m sure you&rsquo;ll love it <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#FightForFreedom<br />\n#StandwithHK"},{"pid":"61c3261e2845ccfceef534e1e4e7b20fc9bae18c","tid":1638764,"uid":11056,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"Thanks bro for opening this post. Looking forward to the questions <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHi world"},{"pid":"2e533fa96d4d2a6380090eea1684fd8474278f69","tid":1638764,"uid":279278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"ec7e61e38c2179d1b5a27075d1d760e4cfba146c","tid":1638764,"uid":243366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"#AskLIHKG1<br /